Class UnmergeResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class UnmergeResponse
extends SiperianResponse
    This response contains the RecordKey for the base object record that is reinstated as a result of the unmerge.

      • getRecordKey

        public RecordKey getRecordKey()
        Returns the RecordKey for the base object record that is reinstated as a result of the unmerge, or or null if the unmerged xref was a direct edit contributed through Load of Put by ROWID that is removed as a result of the unmerge.

        Returns:
        RecordKey of the unmerged record.
